metadata.name: Tió de Nadal 2022 #1
metadata.description:
Caga Tió and his friends arrived a little late this year, but they're still excited to see you and share their adventures! 

Catalonian legend has it that when our wooden friend Tió shows up on the doorstep, if you bring him into your house and keep him warm until the holidays then all the kids get to whack him with sticks while singing until he poops out presents. The more you whack him the more presents he poops. Afterwards, you can burn him and wait patiently for his resurrection next year <3 

A little present to thank you for making my 2022 brighter 🙏🪵

Shit, tió,

hazelnuts and nougats,

do not shit herrings,

they are too salty,

shit nougats

they taste better.

Shit, tió,

almonds and nougats,

and if you don't want to shit

I will hit you with a stick!

Shit, tió!
